text: Terebra luandensis is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Terebridae, the auger snails. The status of this species is uncertain. ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== * Aubry U. 2008. Nuove terebre dall'Angola. Malacologia Mostra Mondiale 59: 14-16 * Terryn Y. & Ryall P. (2014) West African Terebridae, with the description of a new species from the Cape Verde Islands. Conchylia 44(3-4): 27-47 Category:Terebridae Category:Gastropods described in 2008
title: Terebra luandensis
